THIRTIETH ANNUAL Commencement Exercises EAGLEVILLE HIGH SCHOOL SUNDAY AFTERNOON, APRIL 18th 2:30 O'CLOCK WEDNESDAY EVENING, APRIL 21st 8:30 O'CLOCK 1943
GRADUATION EXERCISES WEDNESDAY EVENING Processional-Largo - Handel Song - Class Invocation - Rev. S.H. Parks Song - Grammar School Address - Baxter E. Hobgood Presentation of Medals Presentation of Diplomas Recessional (March Militaire) - Schubert
CLASS ROLL
Wendell Arnold, Wilma Boyce, Harvey Dyer Jr., Emogene Chambliss, Carl Frost, Elma Chick, Leon Lamb, Ethel Drennon, Alvin Pate, Susan Hill, Cannon Pate, Martha Anna Jackson, Billy Simpson, mary Louise Jarrell, Thomas Simpson, Evelyn Patterson, Bill Wilson, Melba Ralston, [and] Alene Scott CLASS OFFICERS Carl Frost - President; Wendell Arnold - Vice-President; Martha Anna Jackson - Secretary; Leon Lamb - Treasurer.
